of the aclu joined mills and myers at a news conference and said 
the treasury department is simply without authority to reach 
directly into the first amendmentprotected activities of americans 
in the united states and prevent them from organizating towards the 
perfectly legal end of travel to vietnam 
in 1977 the treasury department issued regulations exempting 
travel transactions from the embargo and authorizing individuals 
to spend funds incident to travel the march 1988 regulation 
amended this by prohibiting americans in the united states from 
arranging or promoting such travel 
we believe that an attempt to prosecute vietnam veterans for 
