<TEXT>
a white expoliceman who said he 
believes blacks are animals was sentenced to hang thursday for 
killing seven blacks and an indian man in two shooting sprees he 
hoped would provoke a race war 
the killings by barend strydom were committed in an unfeeling 
and coldblooded manner that i have never before experienced or 
heard of said justice louis harms mass murder or racial 
murder will not be tolerated by this court 
in one of south africas most dramatic trials relatives of the 
black victims and white extremists supportive of strydom crowded 
into pretoria supreme court for two weeks to hear testimony about 
the 23yearold defendants racist beliefs 
harms convicted strydom last week of killing seven people and 
