the sun warmed to the occasion thursday 
powering the entries in the first american tour de sol a race for 
solarpowered cars from vermont to massachusetts 
the trip which takes four hours for internal combustionengined 
vehicles will take these competitors four days 
all five entries plus a pintsize speedster driven by a 
