britains merchandise trade deficit widened to 
216 billion pounds 34 billion in april from 168 billion 
pounds 27 billion in march the government said thursday 
the department of trade and industry said the current account 
deficit widened to 166 billion pounds 26 billion from 118 
billion pounds 19 billion a month earlier 
