services overseas investment earnings and official transfer 
payments the government estimates that britains invisible trade 
was in surplus of 500 million pounds 790 million in april 
the figures nearly matched expectations 
since the beginning of 1989 britains merchandise trade deficit 
came to 80 billion pounds 13 billion compared with a deficit 
